-- Editor runs each statement on its own pooled session, so cross-statement
-- tables vanish). Everything runs in ONE statement via CTEs + a data-modifying
-- WITH: existing recipes are UPDATED (matched by name, no duplicates) and new
-- ones are INSERTED. Ingredient lines link to your ingredients table by name
-- (grams always kept). Recipes are shared master recipes (owner_id/place_id null).
-- Safe to re-run.
